Media Personality, Toke Makinwa, has revealed how the Nigerians would have reacted towards International singer, Rihanna’s constant exposure of her baby bump. Recall that the singer has been seen in different outfits revealing her baby bump, which is considered as unusual and bizarre in Nigeria. According to Makinwa in an Instagram story with a picture of Rihanna exposing her baby bump, Nigerians would have called Rihanna out, saying that witches will attack her child because of her dressing. Rihanna May Deliver Baby Girl This Month, Kemi Olunloyo Reveals JUST IN: Rihanna Pregnant, Expecting Child With A$AP She wrote, “If she was Nigerian, world people will say witch will attack the child.”